value.0: A scholar from the city of Calderis with the colors of the Ebon Wyrm guild. She peers interestedly at the pyramid's door.
When an ordinary lantern just won't do it, this lantern seems of high quality and craftsmanship.

Value.value: Ack! You scared me! I thought you were one of those beasts.
I'm trying to get into the pyramid. The door is at once incredibly simple but yet completely obtuse.
There are ruins to the west of here that might hold the key.
My word, you saw WHAT? Erm, I'm not sure if this is a reliable source of information, but if the door opens we are satisfied.
Have you found the way in? Bah, search the ruins to the west!
Now, to delve into ancient depths. This is exciting!
Can you see if you can find a way to open this door?
My scholarly order has a large bounty for you if successful.
